*Radio* da se neko nešto sprema. (He is said to be getting ready for something.)
On *radio* da će doći. (He was heard to be coming.)
Ona *radi* u radio stanici. (She works at the radio station.)
Oni *rado* pričaju o njoj. (They gladly talk about her.)
Ona *radi* kao radio voditelj. (She works as a radio host.)